{"tid":1597344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國電影分享 逆權公民1987 (負能量)","createTime":"2019-09-27T01:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T02:05:40.000Z","uid":261013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a5664f6e2ec5207de2de7f691d05bcb02fec92","tid":1597344,"uid":261013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:50:02.000Z","msg":"尚未睇完不過睇到好心up<br />\n<br />\n改編南韓真實歷史，以「六月民主運動」為背景。1987年1月，22歲大學生朴鍾哲在漢城南營洞受警方的反共調查期間死亡。對共搜查處朴處長指令將屍體火化，但當值的崔檢查官堅持驗屍，結果顯示大學生遭拷打致死，記者尹尚三意外發現死因，事件在各大媒體爆光。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://viu.tv/encore/1-987-when-the-day-comes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2Fencore%2F1-987-when-the-day-comes&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=331ad241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://viu.tv/encore/1-987-when-the-day-comes</a><br />\n<br />\n另外為上次放負道歉，sorry <br />\n本人絕對無意帶風向，並非mom post狗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">榮光歸於義士 榮光歸於香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"4f4227f41754ab0b320abae3510073b8df983d66","tid":1597344,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:05:40.000Z","msg":"攞去print啦<br />\n攞去貼啦<br />\n9月30要全港收皮呀！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/veZcUWn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FveZcUWn.jpg&h=c7dab408&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}